<?xml version="1.0"?>
<guide self="ebuild-writing/functions/pkg_prerm/">
<chapter>
<title>pkg_prerm</title>

<body>
<table>
  <tr>
    <th>函数名</th>
    <ti><c>pkg_prerm</c></ti>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>意义</th>
    <ti>在软件包被卸载之前调用</ti>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>Sandbox</th>
    <ti>关闭</ti>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>所需权限</th>
    <ti>root</ti>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <th>被谁调用</th>
    <ti>ebuild, binary</ti>
  </tr>
</table>
</body>

<section>
<title>默认的 <c>pkg_prerm</c></title>
<body>
<codesample lang="ebuild">
pkg_prerm()
{
    return
}
</codesample>
</body>
</section>

<section>
<title>实例 <c>pkg_prerm</c></title>
<body>
<codesample lang="ebuild">
pkg_prerm() {
    # clean up temp files
    [[ -d "${ROOT}/var/tmp/foo" ]] &amp;&amp; rm -rf "${ROOT}/var/tmp/foo"
}
</codesample>
</body>
</section>

<section>
<title>函数<c>pkg_prerm</c>通常运用</title>
<body>
<p>
函数<c>pkg_prerm</c>用来在卸载软件包之前为系统做一些清理工作。
</p>
</body>
</section>

</chapter>
</guide>
